sourceMeaningMnemonic: <radical>Music</radical> <radical>beans</radical> make farts <kanji>plentiful</kanji>. And lucky for you, you have an <kanji>abundant</kanji> stock of these music beans, so you can eat plenty of them to power your musical bean toots.
meaningInfo: Imagine dancing to your own plentiful bean music as you gorge on the abundant stock of beans.
readingMnemonic: Your music bean farts are too <kanji>plentiful</kanji> to leave your <reading>ho</reading>me (<ja>ほう</ja>). If you tried to leave your home you'd definitely fart all over people outside, so you keep your plentiful farts to yourself.
readingInfo: Be polite! Keep your plentiful farts at home.
